{"tid":562584,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實板燒雞腿包係一個勵志故事","createTime":"2018-02-16T05:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T09:53:14.000Z","uid":14734,"like":130,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c641a3d076ddb351e1b53a44ff65f5dc026cb0a8","tid":562584,"uid":14734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"過年走落街食老m<br />\n咬住個板雞 飲住杯可樂<br />\n諗諗下 板雞又何嘗唔係一個勵志故<br />\n由期間限定變到常設包 <br />\n突然一日取消左 又係群眾壓力下回歸<br />\n到初五仲會華麗轉身做埋24蚊餐<br />\n走過高山低谷 雖然個包愈黎愈細個 <br />\n但口味依舊<br />\n同埋保持住永不放棄既係板雞精神"},{"pid":"ced2e2dd898b87b86066557af848810f65b13ce5","tid":562584,"uid":158977,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"還我Big Mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2e7aa373568dcb94415add607e307252f1d787","tid":562584,"uid":170838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"俾你看透咗人生"},{"pid":"9c2749507b2dd3f3cf3c9ce1642c0fe05e680c57","tid":562584,"uid":62289,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ced2e2dd898b87b86066557af848810f65b13ce5","tid":562584,"uid":158977,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"還我Big Mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"我記得有期 雞翼餐都做過特價餐<br />\n個期食左過百隻雞"},{"pid":"b0edced061555fbbe0bfaa330ef9e6d8b07a831b","tid":562584,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"板雞隻味變左"},{"pid":"f568ae1a0a62908cee0436de28a67773f3516812","tid":562584,"uid":14734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ced2e2dd898b87b86066557af848810f65b13ce5","tid":562584,"uid":158977,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"還我Big Mac<i